### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

###

### Get all posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts

###

### Create post (minimal)
# @name createPost
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "New Post",
  "content": "This is the content of the new post."
}

###

### Create post (lengkap)
# @name createPostFull
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "New Post Full",
  "slug": "new-post-full",
  "content": "This is the content of the new post.",
  "excerpt": "Short description of the post.",
  "status": "DRAFT",
  "featuredImageId": 1,
  "categoryIds": [1, 2]
}

###

### Get post by id
@postId = {{createPost.response.body.data.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}

###

### Update post — judul dan konten
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Updated Post",
  "content": "This is the updated content of the post."
}

###

### Update post — pindah ke review
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "REVIEW"
}

###

### Update post — publish
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "PUBLISHED"
}

###

### Update post — archive
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "ARCHIVED"
}

###

### Update post — ganti kategori
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "categoryIds": [2, 3]
}

###

### Update post — hapus featured image
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "featuredImageId": null
}

###

### Delete post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}

###

### ─── ERROR CASES ──────────────────────────

### Get post — id tidak valid
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/abc

###

### Get post — tidak ditemukan
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/99999

###

### Create post — tanpa title (validasi zod)
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "No title here"
}

###

### Update post — status transition tidak valid (ARCHIVED → DRAFT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "DRAFT"
}

###

### Update post — body kosong (refine zod)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{}